graph LR
    A([Live Log Stream]) --> B[Window Aggregator\n1-minute buckets]
    B --> C[Pattern Parser / Tokenizer]

    subgraph Similarity Engine
        C --> D[Log Vectorizer\nTF-IDF weights]
        D --> E{Cosine Similarity\nvs 30-day baseline}
    end

    subgraph Alarm Output
        E -- "< 0.85 Anomalous" --> F[Flag Drift Event]
        E -- ">= 0.85 Normal"  --> G[Update Baseline Weights]
    end

    F --> H[Cluster Anomaly Groups]
    H --> I[Security Dashboard\nLog Drift Panel]
